  {
    "kind": 1,
    "language": "markdown",
    "value": "### Travail sur les classes disponibles\n\n\n* Noter que manquent les labels",
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "kind": 1,
    "language": "markdown",
    "value": "PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\n\nselect ?class ?classLabel (count(*) as ?number)\nwhere {  \n  graph <https://github.com/lod4hss-projects/workshops/blob/main/DH25-Lisbon/graphs/sdhss-data.md>\n {?s a ?class.\nOPTIONAL {?class rdfs:label ?classLabel}}\n} \ngroup by ?class ?classLabel\norder by desc(?number)\n\n",
    "metadata": {}
  },
